reviewText:
Peach is such a mixed bag, but if you select carefully you can avoid the disappointment and get jewels like this. It's one of the best Peach titles that I have seen and has a great combination of hot models and explicit nudity. A LOT of explicit nudity--way more than I had been expecting and far above the average for Peach.

There are five women here, and every discussion that includes Shay Laren always should start and end with Shay Laren. She is the hottest of the lot but (as has been the case with most Peach DVDs featuring her), she doesn't expose nearly as much as all of the rest of the models. In fact that's my main gripe with this DVD and it's really the only thing that keeps me from giving it five stars. I don't get it--it must be contractual and since she has more name recognition than the rest she probably commands a higher price tag to show all of herself to us. She's still amazing and does full front and rear.

The other models--the phenomenal natural-busted Cassia Riley, mousy-but-kind-of-cute Melissa Jacobs, mankiller Codi Milo and deceptively sweet Lisa Daniels--are all very solid selections from the Peach rotation. Riley and Milo particularly go above and beyond the call of duty here. Jacobs and Riley appear in three vignettes each out of a total of nine (sometimes in tandem with other models). Laren appears twice but both times solo.

The only other negative that I have on this one is that I'm a big fan of natural breasts and only two of the models have those. But there aren't any really distracting, grossly-misshapen jobs here, so it's not a major negative.

Yeah Cassia Riley is simply gorgeous.  Shay Laren is quite nice.  It doesn't even bother with a story so you don't have to pretend to be interested it is just vignette to vignette.  No hardcore action but the girls are hot and ready so if that is your thing this one should be on your radar.

Club Erotique is a DVD video of various girls posing and stripping. The video is very closely done in the style of Penthouse Magazine Video. The video has 9 different scenes covering just under an hour. (About 5-7 minutes per scene or girl) Some of the girls in this DVD are also famous models that have also appeared in either Penthouse Magazine, or from various adult web sites. Such models include Cassia Riley, Shay Laren, and Melissa Jacobs, just to name some of the models in the video.

The DVD contains the movie, photo slideshow, and trailers for other "Peach Entertainment" or "Red Dragon Releasing" videos available wherever adult videos are sold.

Overall it's a nice DVD and good quality video. Personally I don't recommend paying more than $15 for this DVD as it's only just over 1 hour long. (01:03:33) FOR ADULTS ONLY!!!
